### Course Modules API Tests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@courseId = <PLACE_YOUR_COURSE_ID_HERE>
@moduleId = <PLACE_YOUR_MODULE_ID_HERE>
@token = <PLACE_YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN_HERE>

### Create a new module (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/modules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Module 1: Getting Started",
    "description": "This is the first module"
}

### Get all modules for a course
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/modules

### Get a specific module
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/modules/{{moduleId}}

### Update a module (Protected)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/modules/{{moduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Module 1: Introduction",
    "description": "Updated description"
}

### Reorder modules (Protected)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/modules/reorder
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "moduleIds": [
        "{{moduleId}}",
        "<ANOTHER_MODULE_ID>"
    ]
}

### Soft delete a module (Protected)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/modules/{{moduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
